sources.title: Count Five and Die
sources.description: Title: Count Five and Die Summary: American and British counter-espionage combine to convince the Germans the cross-channel invasion will be in the Netherlands instead of France. Directed by: Victor Vicas Actors: Jeffrey Hunter, Annemarie Düringer, Nigel Patrick Production Company: Zonic Productions Release Date: March 1958 (USA) Aspect Ratio: 2.35 : 1 American and British counter-espionage combine to convince the Germans the cross-channel invasion will be in the Netherlands instead of France.
